  - Sacrifice-Death=Sacrifice and Suffering=Sacrifice
By: Rûmi
Format: verse
---
Though one equal to a hundred like me would not have the strength to bear the
  Sea, yet I cannot refrain from the drowning waters of the Sea.

May my soul and mind be a sacrifice to the Sea： this Sea has paid the
  blood-price of mind and soul.
